HEADWORD: Coltish
<hw>Colt"ish</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Like a colt; wanton;
frisky.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>He was all <qex>coltish</qex>, full of ragery.</q>
<rj><qau>Chaucer.</qau></rj></p>

